## 🔔 Phase 5: Realtime Events

### Socket Events to Broadcast:

| Event | Payload | Triggered When |
|-------|---------|---------------|
| `attendance:clock_in` | `{ staffId, staffName, time, dealerId }` | Technician clocks in |
| `attendance:clock_out` | `{ staffId, staffName, time, totalWorkMinutes, dealerId }` | Technician clocks out |
| `attendance:shift_start` | `{ staffId, staffName, time, dealerId }` | Shift started |
| `attendance:shift_end` | `{ staffId, staffName, time, shiftDurationMs, dealerId }` | Shift ended (break) |

### Portal Listener:

Service Admin attendance page listens to these events and auto-updates the technician list without full page refresh.

